While this blog post provides a description of a data exposure discovery involving Deep Root Analytics and the Republican National Committee (RNC) this is no longer an active data breach. As soon as Deep Root Analytics was notified of this publicly exposed information, immediate action was taken, securing the database and preventing further access.
